h of a wide range of DM-electron\ninteractions from the null result of DM search experiments using argon and\nxenon targets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2019 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Aug 2020 09:06:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-20"}
