s\nexpected to get high baryon densities. It is of interest also in the context of\nthe neutron stars, where quark matter might be realized in the core and very\nhigh baryon and isospin densities are attained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Dec 2019 14:35:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-19"}
