 requirements\nis one of its main goals. Those requirements will define the capabilities of\nEST and the post-focus instrument suite. The technical requirements for the\nfinal design of EST will be derived from the SRD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Dec 2019 15:10:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-19"}
